sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>9000 or 443/TCP<br/>TLS configurable
    participant WFC as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant StepPod as Pipeline Step Pod
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,PA: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(DSPA api subresource)
    KRBP->>API: Proxied request<br/>8888/TCP, TLS (service-ca)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>3306/TCP, TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: DB password (Secret)
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    API-->>KRBP: Pipeline created
    KRBP-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,PA: Pipeline Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs
    Route->>KRBP: Forward
    KRBP->>API: Create Run
    API->>DB: Store run metadata
    API-->>KRBP: Run created (Workflow submitted)

    WFC->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow events
    WFC->>K8s: Create/Update step pods

    StepPod->>MLMD: Log artifacts/executions<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>NetworkPolicy controlled
    StepPod->>API: Report status<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    PA->>API: Sync Argo status → KFP DB<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)

    Note over User,PA: Flow 2: MLMD Metadata Access (External)

    participant MDRoute as MLMD Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MDProxy as MLMD kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    User->>MDRoute: GET metadata<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token
    MDRoute->>MDProxy: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    MDProxy->>MDProxy: SubjectAccessReview
    MDProxy->>Envoy: Proxied<br/>9090/TCP HTTP
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC request<br/>8080/TCP TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Query lineage<br/>3306/TCP TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Results
    MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
    Envoy-->>MDProxy: HTTP response
    MDProxy-->>MDRoute: Response
    MDRoute-->>User: Metadata response

    Note over User,PA: Flow 3: Managed Pipelines Validation

    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
    participant OCI as OCI Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    DSPO->>OCI: Fetch managed-pipelines.json<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: Keychain (pull secrets)
    OCI-->>DSPO: managed-pipelines.json
    DSPO->>DSPO: Validate CR pipeline names<br/>against manifest (10min cache)
    DSPO->>API: Deploy with init container<br/>mounting managed pipelines
